Description:
The Perfect Package
Proudly positioned in one of the finest pocket of Taylors Lakes amongst other prestigious homes and only minutes from all major amenities sits this gorgeous family home, on a commanding allotment of approx 650sqm. Greeted with a stunning façade and warm entrance with formal lounge and dining room, leading into the heart of the home, a spacious kitchen, brimming with natural light overlooking a huge meals and family area adjoining separate rumpus room. Step outside to a gorgeous undercover entertainment area and stunning solar heated/salt chlorinated swimming pool, perfect for year round enjoyment. Living quarters provide the family with four great sized bedrooms, master with walk in robe and ensuite, upstairs kids retreat, study room and downstairs powder room. Extras include; ducted heating, evaporative cooling and double garage with drive through access. The family will love every element of this gorgeous family home. Contact Andrew or Justin to arrange and inspection.

Description:
Inspection Cancelled - UNDER CONTRACT
When all the best and brightest ideas are so beautifully combined into such a scintillating contemporary package all you can do is wish it was yours. Now, it can be!
This brilliant residence reveals a total commitment to quality and fabulous open spaces throughout. Features formal lounge with cathedral ceilings, formal dining or potential 4th bedroom or study which flows through to the stunning renovated kitchen with stone benchtops and quality cooking appliances with double oven.
Tucked away to the rear are 3 large bedrooms, 2 with walk-in robes, master with full ensuite, updated bathroom, and a large family area which can accommodate a large gathering. The undercover alfresco provides great shade all year round. You better like to entertain, because your friends and family will start inviting themselves over when they find out you have a gorgeous solar heated pool and a generous lawn for the kids.
This is simply a stunning home with no compromise. Finishing touches include ducted heating, evaporative cooling, double crossover, secured undercover parking with a massive driveway for your boat and/or caravan.
A superb entertainers lifestyle with the allure of a tranquil setting right next to the newly upgraded Taylors Lakes Linear Park. After dinner, enjoy a leisurely walk around the lake, feed the ducks and let your kids tire themselves out on the playground.
Also zoned and walking distance to Taylors Lakes Primary and Secondary College and within minutes drive to Watergardens Shopping Centre and Calder Freeway.
Our signs are everywhere... winningAS

Description:
A sublime, single level family haven.
Behind its sleek contemporary exterior this comprehensively renovated three bedroom plus study, two bathroom residence of superb proportions caters effortlessly to modern family desires. A passion for perfection delivers a free flowing layout comprising elegant living, dining zones, light filled family space and gourmet kitchen leading to a fabulous alfresco entertaining deck. Showcasing exceptional attention to detail, with stone island, custom made glass splashback, Ilve cooker, dishwasher and walk-in-pantry, the kitchen is high end. The master bedroom is discreetly placed at the front, with walk-in-robe and stone ensuite. Two further bedrooms offer built-in-robes. Highlighted by luxury bathroom with rainfall shower, powder room, large laundry, refrigerated cooling, ducted heating, plantation shutters, vast storage, automated double garage and security system. Enviably placed to St Christophers Primary, shops, cafés, Westfield, La Manna, Keilor Road precinct, public and private schools, parks / trails and freeways.

Description:
Real appeal near everything.
Convenience is key a stroll to everything from local shops and cafes to transport, schools and parks, this contemporary three bedroom home extends an invitation to come in and relax. Generous and open by design, the floor plan leads past sleeping quarters to a kitchen, meals and living featuring a dishwasher and 90cm stainless steel appliances, including a canopy rangehood and stove with gas cooktop/fan forced electric oven. Wide glass aspects enhance the living area, one leading to a landscaped and easily maintained courtyard. Complete with a central dual entry bathroom, hosting a shower, separate bath, mirrored cabinets, toilet and vanity with semi-recessed basin, it also offers a powder room and laundry. Built-in robes, heating, cooling, a rainwater tank, individual driveway and remote garage further appeal, as does close proximity to freeway access, Essendon Fields and Keilor Road. Ideal for a wide range of buyers, this is one home set to find many admirers.

Description:
Entry-Level Excellence or Downsize Delight!
Positioned for absolute convenience in the heart of Keilor East, this 3BR single-level residence offers broad appeal with its spacious floorplan, excellent presentation and immaculate low-maintenance surrounds. More house than villa, the home's free-flowing interior comprises a master bedroom with WIR and private ensuite, two additional bedrooms, main central bathroom and separate WC. Add to this a spacious front lounge leading through to the open dining area and spotless kitchen with tiled splashbacks and gas cooktop. Ducted heating throughout, the home also includes a full-size laundry, plus a sunny back garden with undercover patio and rear access into the remote-control double garage. Walking distance to Phillip Road/Buckley Street buses and Rosehill Park, it's also close to Milleara Shopping Centre, primary and secondary schools as well as easy access to the Calder Freeway and Western Ring Road.

Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.

Description:
Single-Level Style in a Prime Position
Modern low-maintenance living at its brilliant best, this feature-packed 3BR home stands out from the crowd with its design excellence, quality inclusions and idyllic location in the very heart of Keilor East. Immediately impressive, the home's free-flowing interior comprises a large master bedroom with WIR and private ensuite, two additional bedrooms (both with BIRs), main central bathroom and separate WC. Bathed in natural light, the spacious open-plan living/dining area is enhanced by a stone-bench kitchen with soft-close drawers, stainless steel cooking appliances and dishwasher. Square-set ceilings throughout, the home also features split-system heating and cooling (living area and all bedrooms), efficient LED lighting, solid hardwood floors and a full-size laundry. Stacker doors lead out to a wide rear courtyard complete with large undercover entertaining deck, plus the added appeal of an internally-accessed garage (r/c) and additional driveway parking space. Walking distance to Centreway cafes and shops, local buses (on Clarks Road), popular primary and secondary schools (including PEGS), Steele Creek trails and the open spaces of Spring Gully Reserve as well as easy freeway access. Simply move in and start living!
* Jellis Craig Coronavirus Update*
At Jellis Craig the health and wellbeing of our clients and staff is our highest priority.
In light of the recent Coronavirus outbreak, we are taking measures to protect our clients and staff from coming into contact with the virus, and request that you do not attend an Open for Inspection if you have:
- Tested positive to Coronavirus
- Symptoms associated with Coronavirus

- Recently been overseas
- Agreed to any self-isolation conditions
We also ask that you maintain adequate social distancing from anyone attending the open for inspection, including other prospective clients and Jellis Craig sales teams and where possible refrain from touching surfaces within the property. We also appreciate your understanding if you are requested to wait outside to reduce the number of people in the property at a time.
Thank you for your understanding.

Description:
Exceptional Space and Family Flexibility
Surrounded by other quality homes in a secluded Keilor Park cul-de-sac, this distinctive residence provides a ready-to-enjoy lifestyle with its wonderfully versatile design and quality features throughout - perfect for families that love to entertain! Beyond the attractive rendered facade, discover a light-filled interior showcasing four bedrooms (extra-large master with WIR and private ensuite) and two additional bathrooms - one on each level. Multiple living zones include formal lounge and dining, vast rumpus area (upstairs) and open-plan family/meals area enhanced by a well-appointed kitchen with breakfast bar, dishwasher and stainless steel cooking appliances. Other highlights of the home include ducted heating and split-system a/c, alarm, ducted vacuum, ornate ceilings and solid timber floors, NBN connection, large laundry and under-stair storeroom, front balcony and rear terrace. Step outside to a wonderfully private backyard with established gardens, undercover patio and gazebo, plus the added advantage of an internally-accessed double garage with adjoining workshop and kitchenette. Spacious and Versatile Low-Maintenance Perfection.
A perfect combination of contemporary class and easy-living excellence, this distinctive double-storey home presents a ready-to-enjoy lifestyle opportunity with its family proportions, premium features and prime position in one of Niddries best streets. On its own separately-titled block with no shared land, the homes beautifully-appointed interior showcases three genuinely large bedrooms (downstairs master with walk in robe and stylish ensuite), main bathroom and guest powder room (third toilet). Multiple living zones include a light-filled lounge, retreat (upstairs) with built-in study alcove, spacious open-plan living/dining area enhanced by a superb stone-bench kitchen complete with Fisher & Paykel cooking appliances and double dish drawers. Other highlights include ducted heating/refrigerated cooling, gas-stone fireplace, ducted vacuum, Spotted Gum solid timber floors, laundry with ironing cupboard and under-stair storeroom. Double sliding doors (from the living area) reveal a fabulous entertainers courtyard with expansive decking, undercover BBQ area, built-in bench seating, integrated lighting and high fences for absolute privacy, plus an oversized remote double garage with internal entry. Description:
Family Entertainer with Flair and Flexibility
Occupying a wonderfully wide allotment with Keilor-edge convenience, this impeccable single-level residence delivers a wonderfully versatile family environment thanks to its multiple living zones, quality enhancements and expansive garden surrounds. A home that's ready to simply move in and enjoy, it's free-flowing interior showcases four generous bedrooms (master with WIR), large home office, along with a contemporary ensuite, equally-stylish main bathroom and separate WC - all with floor-to-ceiling tiles. The front lounge and dining leads through to the open family/meals area accompanied by a granite-bench kitchen with breakfast bar, stainless steel cooking appliances and Bosch dishwasher, plus the added appeal of a vast rear living room with high vaulted ceilings and an abundance of natural light. Other stand-out features include ducted heating and split-system air conditioning, new carpets, efficient LED lighting and stylish plantation shutters across the front, as well as a family-sized laundry with ample cupboard space. Step outside to a fabulous al-fresco style entertaining area complete with outdoor spa and mains-connected BBQ, plus a wide backyard with lush lawn area, established perimeter gardens, large storage shed and remote-control double garage with internal entry. Moments from parkland and endless walking/cycling trails, it also offers close proximity to popular schools including Overnewton College, public transport, local shopping precincts and easy freeway access.
